data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Edmond, OK! This stunning 3 bed, 2 bath gem has a modern open concept design. The spacious kitchen with a breakfast bar seamlessly flows into the inviting living room, creating an ideal space for entertaining. Located in the sought-after Deer Creek School District, this property offers excellent conveniences with a private ambiance as it sits next to a green belt, creek & pond. Other updates/features include: Water Softener (2020), Tile in primary bedroom (2020), CCTV security cameras & modem, Private water well, and all gas appliances. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this place your own!
